Subject: [PATCH 1/4] =?UTF-8?q?feat(quiz):=20grading=20engine=20=E2=80=94?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20partial=20credit,=20knowledge=20goals,=20question=20pools?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- multi-select tasks earn partial credit: points * max(0, (correct
  selections - wrong selections) / total correct); single-choice stays
  all-or-nothing; wrong selections are penalized so select-everything
  earns nothing
- tasks can be tagged with one of the guide's knowledge goals; grading
  aggregates earned/total points per goal into goalBreakdown
- exercises can define a question pool: sanitizeExerciseForClient draws
  poolSize random questions per fetch (rng injectable for tests) and
  reports poolTotal for UI transparency; grading validates the
  submitted subset and grades exactly those questions, failing
  gracefully (ExerciseGradingError -> user-facing message) on a
  malformed submission
- gradeTask extracted as the single per-task scoring function (shared
  with analytics); 23 engine tests cover all of the above
